Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:08.96,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片輕描淡寫地講述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.25,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  一起吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  今天沒帶來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點去比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思你們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼幫我帶個牛奶咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶茶和牛奶咖啡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:33.47,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要把我親手做的便當交給南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:49.45,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是把我親手做的便當給南春香吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:00:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把便當還我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然忘了享受料理的真正目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開便當可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回想一次  你真正想傳達給春香的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正想傳達的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快些擦乾的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必著急這汗還有的流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在社團活動結束後讓南春香替我拭去汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那就需要把春香拉進我們女子排球部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先謝謝了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香  不來打排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香去買麵包了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃麵包會營養失調的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香不可能不知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  今天只是偶爾忘了做飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香在作為學生的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是撫養兩個女兒的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣食和學業並存並不是那麼容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是女兒而是妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此  我能支援她就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的料理  我的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是脫衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上為你製作最棒的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.97,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
