Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也不參加社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得為家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家中有幾人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常不去社團露面是因為要給家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我考慮了下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你能專心於社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來為你的家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上今天已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便當的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梅雨的季節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物中毒必須嚴防
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也沒有疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便當特別加入了大量的醋和生薑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意  作為排球部部長我只是做了理所應當的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  接去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長  我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  說理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受了這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會招來某些人的不好的誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的誤解是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:05:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我不去追問你的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想讓家人吃上熱騰騰的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去後想好好地做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱騰騰的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人其樂融融地吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是名為家人的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來剛才你說了「啊  對了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忽然想起了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有想起來什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不繼續深入家庭的話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但隨時都可以來找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人給做飯的話的確是很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓成熟的女性給做飯的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  成熟的料理的做法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的是「如何讓自己變成熟」和「如何做出好吃的料理」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨意混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我沒有在問夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼成熟地去做料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  裸體圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天才嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對變態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我充斥著無所不能的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間提高料理的水準很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有誰作為特定的對像的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去問問這個人的喜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡甜的或是辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從這裡開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對方的喜好清楚地知道了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以來找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地詢問喜好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜還是辣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決心自己做料理的堅定地眼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡超甜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你們女子排球部做的特製便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺噁心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我做的還好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個雨什麼時候才能停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  已經第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田已經是第幾次問這句話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  第幾次了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  你討厭下雨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是討厭下雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不盡情享受現在的梅雨季節會很吃虧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣去享受？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是濺到水了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.63,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說內田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來追我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕了一身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也向我道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪內田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你們兩個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後千秋也加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了大家都去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田糾結於下雨的問題才會變得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪冬馬把水濺在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互相玩水  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後千秋都用傘玩高爾夫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺都濺濕了也都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  春香你剛才說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣服都不幹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的衣服不夠給她們換的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  所以要把我的衣服拿出來給她們穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我明天就沒有衣服穿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天其它的衣服不就乾了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪裡來的保證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你的借她們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的衣服尺寸上很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也不會奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的「不是什麼大事」多數時候都是大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得浴巾都拿去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾的一條都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…用什麼擦身子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底只要把校服弄乾不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會這麼快乾的  再說也沒有內衣換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那春香的借她們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸會不合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾應該也還沒乾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她們要用什麼來擦身子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在浴巾的替代品到來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受泡澡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別玩了這裡很窄的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢淋我  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒潑到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要洗的東西又增加了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會乾了  再等一等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會這樣就做些其他的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  內田來玩摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要享受當下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣服乾之前就安安靜靜地等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  請您務必讓雨雲打道回府
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多開始想念藍天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的話一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天還要和藤岡踢足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別祈禱  也別拜我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  你也說說她們讓她們冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你千秋  這樣下去明天就沒有衣服換了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  連你也這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
