Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.85,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}勇者著迷于財寶！！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.90,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}魔王  現身！！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上試著煎了荷包蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得沒做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼個沒做好法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  總覺得還是生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說連半生不熟都還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太著急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡吃熟透的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得自己現在快被曬熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  雖說好久都沒有出太陽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還真像夏天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  雖然我也不討厭半生不熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：雙關語，也可以理解成不怎麼曬太陽的，後續還有幾個也同為雙關語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是在說荷包蛋嗎  還是說曬太陽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說哪件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？喜歡熟透的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雙關語：曬得黝黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:15:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那個…不討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  不討厭熟透的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雙關語：曬得黝黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過每個人對荷包蛋的熟度都有各自的喜好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人喜好…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  不覺得保阪皮膚很白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是排球部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉長得也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只煎單面  翻面起鍋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.78,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sunny side up…turn over…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sunny side up:美國人喜歡的荷包蛋的煎法。\N只煎一面另一面保持生的樣子直接上桌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只煎單面  翻面起鍋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只煎單面  翻面起鍋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只煎單面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格方面就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻面起鍋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  抱歉打擾你自言自語了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在演練為南春香做早餐的荷包蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她並不討厭熟透的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雙關語：曬得黝黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  原來是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢  你是指哪方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是荷包蛋的火候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是男生的膚色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然問的有點突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡幾分熟的荷包蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你喜歡幾分熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡不太熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  沒有曬得太黑的我就是剛剛好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對  現在是在討論荷包蛋的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到荷包蛋  就覺得…就覺得很想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種想要吃掉我的眼神看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃荷包蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把蛋煎熟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要翻面  煎雙面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個部分都煎到才行 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這裡最重要的  就是翻面的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把兩面煎得恰到好處的我獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到適合用來盛獻給南春香的新料理的器皿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我自己做了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這是保阪你做的？做得挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  終於做了一個自己比較滿意的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顏色無法用語言表達…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是白色嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那形狀  是為了我的料理重複計算得出的全新…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是圓形嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢  你要盛怎樣的料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…奇怪  難道在生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣？你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是心胸寬廣的男人保阪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色也好形狀也好  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據當事人的感覺來判斷就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要拘泥於用途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  去問問其他人用這個來盛什麼好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是保阪  你想去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正等著你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你們  最棒的料理所需要的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛情…之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  啊不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這種情況下不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒的料理需要的是最棒的器皿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這個  對不起我沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我做出了最棒的盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是保阪學長做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺做的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  的確做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了做這個花了很久的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是選土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從各種各樣的陶土裡  我選擇了白陶土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱之為高嶺土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被譽為西洋白瓷最經典的邁森瓷器的主要原材料 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這獨特的白皙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨一無二的白皙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及無與倫比的白皙  諸如此類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂燒制陶器也與料理相通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要充分理解並活用陶土的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能燒制出專屬於我的瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我選擇了能使陶土更加閃亮的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反復試驗  最後呈現出的就是這種色澤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽含初夏般耀眼的陽光以及溫柔的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才得以成就出如此細膩的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是一定要用話語來形容這個色澤的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是銀色！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來光輝四射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且形狀也是  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若將料理比作人的話  那麼器皿就相當於衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若人的姿色勝過衣服就顯得落魄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而衣服的華麗勝過人則顯得滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理與容器應該是對等的並互相襯托才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以語言來形容這襯托出料理之美的容器的形狀是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樸素的實用性之美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既簡約又完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就出在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認為應該用它來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來燒水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會參考你們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  那是什麼  水壺？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼覺得麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱水麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟能否僅憑熱水就為南春香帶來笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我吧  我的水壺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  盤子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  幫我看著三分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4  5  6…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的面看起來很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會要不要也嘗一口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就換著吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我看著鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15  16  17…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.78,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈也來換著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:36.61,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看著鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22  23  24  25 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,26  27  28  29
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三分鐘到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別想蒙混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:35.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(900,600)\fs45}要開始做中式涼麵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  請告訴我如此能變成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算變成熟然後做些奇怪的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  要開始做中式涼麵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我變得更擅長做飯
